TNK-BP to Pay $1 Billion for Brazil Oil Project, Kommersant Says

-- B y   D e n i s   M a t e r n o v s k y
-- 
2011-05-26T03:54:28Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-26/tnk-bp-to-pay-1-billion-for-brazil-oil-project-kommersant-says.html
TNK-BP,  BP Plc (BP/) ’s Russian venture, is
in talks with  Brazil ’s  HRT Participacoes em Petroleo SA (HRTP3)  to buy a
45 percent stake in its oil and gas project in the South
American country’s Solimoes region, Kommersant reported.  The Russian company may pay as much as $1 billion for the
asset after HRT repurchases the stake from its current partner
in the development Petra Energia SA, the Moscow-based newspaper
said, citing unidentified people with knowledge of the deal.  Click here for web link  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Denis Maternovsky at 
 dmaternovsky@bloomberg.net  